phliker.com.service

Interface Service

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CacheService, FlickrService

    public interface Service
    A service interface for the Phliker application. The service may be a real service, or a service which modifies some other underlying service (for example providing a cache layer).
    Author:
    Sarvar Nishonboyev
